### 用户相关接口测试

### 获取用户列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 按条件查询用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users?name_like=user&status=1&pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 获取单个用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

### 创建用户
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "test_user",
    "password": "123456",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "status": 1
}

### 更新用户
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin_updated",
    "email": "admin_updated@example.com",
    "status": 1
}

### 删除用户
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/3
Accept: application/json

### 文章相关接口测试

### 获取文章列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 按条件查询文章
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?title_like=Article&status=1&user_id=1&pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 获取单个文章
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/1
Accept: application/json

### 创建文章
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Test Article",
    "content": "This is a test article content.",
    "user_id": 1,
    "status": 1
}

### 更新文章
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/articles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Updated Article",
    "content": "This is the updated article content.",
    "status": 1
}

### 删除文章
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/articles/3
Accept: application/json 